snippet.title: Moto Racer 3 Gameplay
snippet.description:
Moto Racer 3 Playstation Gameplay

Game is really addictive, I really enjoy playing this game using analog as throttle is really fun, you need to choose Team wisely in this game different motorcycle behave differently and setups are key in this game as well.
 There are couple of game modes in this game and all of them are fun there is even drag racing in this game
This game is rare PS1 game that supports 16:9

Catch up with me on Twitter
https://twitter.com/#!/Studio76HD
